    A data set for tracking HealthTrackerType.ECG.

    Measured ECG data list has 5 or 10 DataPoint depending on a sensor's operation status.
    If list size is not 5, it means that 10 DataPoint is received.

    In case of 5 DataPoints:

      List's each DataPoint Included values
      1st DataPoint ECG
      PPG_GREEN
      LEAD_OFF
      SEQUENCE
      MAX_THRESHOLD
      MIN_THRESHOLD
      2nd DataPoint ECG
      3rd DataPoint ECG
      4th DataPoint ECG
      5th DataPoint ECG

    In case of 10 DataPoints, the list has the following 5 DataPoints more:

      List's each DataPoint Included values
      6st DataPoint ECG
      PPG_GREEN
      7nd DataPoint ECG
      8rd DataPoint ECG
      9th DataPoint ECG
      10th DataPoint ECG
